  "content": "<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"elev/20150626summ.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:85%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"elev/20150626elev.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:85%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThe morning would present two approximaetly five mile climbs up to the pass with a short section for\n\t\t\t\t\t\trecovery in between.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tIn general the roads in Wyoming were very rideable. With the exception of some really steep sections that\n\t\t\t\t\t\twas true\n\t\t\t\t\t\tfor this section.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic02.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tStarting the day the same way I started most days - me and my shadow.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic03.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"95%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThe initial stages were really wooded so not many pictures. I was mostly trying to make sure\n\t\t\t\t\t\tI stayed on the purple line because I didn't have the cue sheets for this section. The cuesheets were pretty\n\t\t\t\t\t\tspare in their descriptions.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThis is the section between the two climbs. The road prior to this was one of the toughest I covered. Very\n\t\t\t\t\t\tsteep,\n\t\t\t\t\t\tvery torn up. I couldn't see how an ATV could pass through.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic04.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">Wide open roads - only a few Quads out today\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">On top of the world - part 1</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel1\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel1\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic05b.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                              class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Top of Devils Hole Trail</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>View west</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic05c.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                       class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Top of Devils Hole Trail</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>View south</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic05d.jpg\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                       class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Top of Devils Hole Trail</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>View east</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel1\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a cla