 north</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic11.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                       class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Top of Union Pass area 3</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>View south</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel2\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                        <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                        </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.container -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tCame thru this gate to rejoin the original TD trail\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic13.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tStill pretty close to the top ...\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic14.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t... and mountains all around.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic15.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">Still on top of the divide\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic12.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">Don't forget to stop and smell the flowers\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tI was really happy to be up here. The road to this point had not been easy but getting to this spot really\n\t\t\t\t\t\tconfirmed\n\t\t\t\t\t\twhy I had decided to do this trip. I was amazed again and again during the five plus hours it took me to go\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthrough this section.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic16.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Back to the flats</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThe last 40 miles was rolling downhill and south through wide open spaces. The Wind River Range was to the\n\t\t\t\t\t\teast\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic22.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">Coming off the gravel and back onto a real road.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tI stopped to take a break in the shade of a park bathroom building which was the only shade for miles.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tI was joined by a couple who shared what shade there was.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"carousel3\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"0\" class=\"active\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li data-target=\"#carousel3\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-inner\" role=\"listbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item active\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic17.JPG\" alt=\"First slide image\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                              class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Wyoming transition</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic18.JPG\" alt=\"Second slide image\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                       class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>From the mountains</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic19.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                       class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>to the desert</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item\"><img src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic20.JPG\" alt=\"Third slide image\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                       class=\"center-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"carousel-caption\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Rolling toward Pinedale</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>4</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"left carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel3\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sr-only\">Previous</span></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"right carousel-control\" href=\"#carousel3\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\">\n                                <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                                </span><span class=\"sr-only\">Next</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Pinedale, WY - A nice hotel, laundry and a meal</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 blog-post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/tourdivide/day18/day18pic21.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">Nicest bed since Helena\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tStayed at the Hampton Inn in Pinedale. I had missed the turn to go off the main road and through town.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tI realized it after finishing the last hill of the day so ended up taking a highway the last 3 miles.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tI met Andrew from NZ for dinner. He had ridden through Yellowstone and Jackson for the past few days.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWith the Wyoming desert coming up for the next 3 days I was glad to have another rider in the vicinity.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWe would end up mostly in the same places until July 5th.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tJune 26 - ~83 miles - Lava Mtn Lodge across Union Pass to Pinedale, WY\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=z16rO1nf9OsU.kQFVh1gMgHlU&usp=sharing\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSee full screen map\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</div><!-- /.blog-main -->\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /.blog-post -->\n\t\t</div><!-- /.row -->\n\t</div><!-- /.container -->"
}